We add this after setting \hsize:
    \advance\hsize by-\QUIRE
and this to output routine:
    \ifodd\pageno\else\hoffset=\QUIRE\fi

Connect the pages with thread and needle by making 5 holes and cut protruding parts of pages.

------------------------

QUIRE.tex is used here just as a demo - because стихи.tex does not have too much pages
(if there are too much pages, there will be a big gap between central pages).
